.TH CASTERS-COMPENDIUM 1 "July 2026" "Caster's Compendium 0.1.4" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
casters-compendium \- build and export Caster Chronicles decks
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B casters-compendium
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B Caster's Compendium
is a desktop card browser and deck builder for Caster Chronicles. It imports
and exports Speedrobo-compatible text decklists, creates Tabletop Simulator
image sheets, and installs complete decks directly into Tabletop Simulator.
Card searches can be filtered by rules keywords extracted from the current card
ability data.
.PP
An internet connection is required during the first launch to download and
prepare the card database.
.SH FILES
Application data is stored under Fyne's per-user configuration directory for
the application ID
.BR io.github.hybriduofa.casterdeckbuilder .
.SH HOMEPAGE
https://github.com/HybridUofA/casters-compendium
